========================================
ZAGENT

----------------------------------------
PURPOSE

Move and resize the frontmost window by pressing a key combination.

----------------------------------------
VERSION

0.0
Do not distribute.

----------------------------------------
AUTHOR

Mietek Bak
mietek@gmail.com


========================================
BASIC USAGE

----------------------------------------
KEY COMBINATION     EFFECT

fn + S              Full screen
fn + A              Left half
fn + D              Right half
fn + W              Top half
fn + X              Bottom half
fn + Q              Top left quarter
fn + E              Top right quarter
fn + Z              Bottom left quarter
fn + C              Bottom right quarter
fn + 1              Screen 1
fn + 2              Screen 2
...
fn + 9              Screen 9


========================================
ADVANCED USAGE

----------------------------------------
KEY COMBINATION     EFFECT

fn + S              2/2 horizontal, anchored center
fn + S, S           2/3 horizontal, anchored center
fn + S, S, S        2/4 horizontal, anchored center
...

fn + A              1/2 horizontal, anchored left
fn + A, A           1/3 horizontal, anchored left, index 1
fn + A, D           1/3 horizontal, anchored left, index 2
fn + A, A, A        1/4 horizontal, anchored left, index 1
fn + A, A, D        1/4 horizontal, anchored left, index 2
fn + A, D, D        1/4 horizontal, anchored left, index 3
...

fn + 1, A           Screen 1, 1/2 horizontal, anchored left
...
